</title>
<subSubSection id="DD07FDC9F1416C908B116FC711B9F064" pageId="null" pageNumber="193" type="description">
<paragraph id="F6BFDB0BCB249DB7E8D53D413E4B8071" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="0E3BC3731F14B5751883FEC25F047B05" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Diplotaxis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="193" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="muralis">
<emphasis id="68A059AAEEF438D4ADBDD44A5914E35C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">D. muralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2) durch folgende Merkmale: Stengel meist kahl; Blattabschnitte und 
<normalizedToken id="49B70D772A4A072DBBEA0252EE10C6D7" originalValue="Zähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Zaehne</normalizedToken>
fast waagrecht abstehend. 
<emphasis id="4CD5186A3862F5A330D63DDF46318A0D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">
<normalizedToken id="013E996FDCB3F992E07E382992C9C42D" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
⅔- 
<emphasis id="B327D224BBC3E4AA53C878CBF8D8E470" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">
1mal so lang wie der Kelch; 
<normalizedToken id="85C5431793FE99A61B33B3C554B9C5B7" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="661326507347CCC7BDCB6ED5B16C04A9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">
2,5 mm lang, kahl; 
<normalizedToken id="E93891BECF34D7975BE9F7DD7EF464E1" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
3
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="DCB25D826B28E395C48E6466ACB3D1F8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">4 mm lang;</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="29BDC41664D8B3C30B539079CDE19188" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
1-3,5 cm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="B09094D794E6A14EA457D95157690B6E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="EB67BB73AE8DF3BAAA8D9EADD7D425E7" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="7C7CD13C2EA3993C3C576BBEC31C9358" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="455D6764375A6850C96606F60D7497CB" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">
<emphasis id="4948BB9FEB8B7F9CC42B8E3C596BBC7E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Zytologische Angaben. 2n ca. 20:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischem Garten (Manton 1932).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="677592B7B97B0DAA6867333EEF02A00D" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">
<emphasis id="ED7D07024A52C61A2F9E21F20A8B9215" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Offene, lockere, 
<normalizedToken id="1D4332D978C98E501B81997D536CF14E" originalValue="nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="0507C16FC6C177BE358E45FC74285386" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in milden Lagen. Weinberge, 
<normalizedToken id="739C9AA846B9F24882787809DE3656F8" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="65D010DAD3663D6D2F19ECE2BD989CE8" originalValue="Schuttplätze" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Schuttplaetze</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="05903196BCE6832EEC0178830135D580" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">
<emphasis id="36541CD7C842B3DE43E9093A2661F54F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="B5D390417B3B2E55388D2A642723A4F4" originalValue="Südeuropa" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Suedeuropa</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="0B20264733A17C2698C5626C8415BBCF" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Lothringen, Maingebiet, Alpen, 
<normalizedToken id="D99B236676A8EDEC51D48639E4001EC1" originalValue="Rumänien" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Rumaenien</normalizedToken>
); Kleinasien, 
<normalizedToken id="B0560DD439F6AFB5754E629C2C7FAC50" originalValue="Palästina" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Palaestina</normalizedToken>
, Nordwestafrika. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel et al. (1965). - Im Gebiet: Oberrheinische Tiefebene (Kaiserstuhl), 
<normalizedToken id="19F6B639A56B0224CC07EA7B4850F7C9" originalValue="südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Jura (Ruffieux, 
<normalizedToken id="8410CA67F1D1A0E195EE6EB40928751F" originalValue="Serrières" pageId="null" pageNumber="193">Serrieres</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
